{"tid":1239440,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥四點見記者 紙巾早已預備","createTime":"2019-06-18T07:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T07:21:38.000Z","uid":60306,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a1482b706789cb5acf4e8bd56bc05a48ea2f24cc","tid":1239440,"uid":60306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T07:20:00.000Z","msg":"【即時】(14:52) 行政長官林鄭月娥將在四點見記者，就《逃犯條例》修訂事宜再向記者交代。在政府總部演講廳的講台上，記者發現，職員分別已準備好一包和兩盒紙巾，其中該包紙巾內的三張紙巾更是「全數外露」。有在場的記者笑言，屆時將會上演「眼淚攻勢」。<br />\n<br />\n#獨媒報導 #逃犯條例<br />\n追蹤最新消息：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/inmediahknet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finmediahknet&d=b2hjM7c23Ds3Tm%2B3KbcyAcdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=944a176a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/inmediahknet</a><br />\n報導有價，請月捐支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2W46Sy2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2W46Sy2&d=b2hjM7c23Ds3Tm%2B3KbcyAcdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=4a73dae6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2W46Sy2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c50ee5d0e40f994ee61ec6ae8c6ff8bc7718b4","tid":1239440,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T07:21:13.000Z","msg":"預告定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ed34866f9c704ea596639343b01a806544d96b","tid":1239440,"uid":135798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T07:21:38.000Z","msg":"有在場的記者笑言，屆時將會上演「眼淚攻勢」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}